BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:尖帽子的魔法工房 1
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260406
DTSTAMP;VALUE=DATE:20260723
UID:377130-1-zbodo
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:「开始的魔法」\n\n\n众人皆以为魔法是与生俱
